title: Judge Dredd v05 - The American Way of Death (2014) (Digital) (DR
description:
Judge Dredd v05 - The American Way of Death (2014) (Digital) (DR & Quinch-Empire)


Dredd's most vicious and unstoppable enemies - the Dark Judges - are clawing their way into Mega-City One, determined to transform it into a new city of the dead. But the only thing more horrifying than the Dark Judges' onslaught are the drastic measures the Justice Department is willing to take to repel them
